---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About Dr. Stuteville | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Learn about Dr. Taylor Stuteville, PsyD — a clinical psychologist specializing in therapy for first responders, anxiety, depression, and chronic pain in Overland Park, KS." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<!-- Page Hero -->
		<section class="page-hero">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label">About</p>
				<h1>Dr. Taylor Stuteville, PsyD</h1>
				<p class="page-hero-desc">Clinical Psychologist &mdash; Overland Park, KS</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Bio Section -->
		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="bio-grid">
					<div class="bio-photo">
						<div class="bio-photo-placeholder">
							<svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
								<circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Professional Headshot</span>
						</div>
						<div class="credentials-card">
							<h4>Credentials</h4>
							<ul>
								<li><strong>PsyD</strong> &mdash; Kansas City University</li>
								<li><strong>BA, Psychology</strong> &mdash; University of Kansas</li>
								<li><strong>Licensed Psychologist</strong> &mdash; State of Kansas</li>
								<li><strong>Practice</strong> &mdash; Slate Psychology, LLC</li>
								<li><strong>Affiliation</strong> &mdash; Enso Therapy Group</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="bio-content">
						<h2>A Commitment to Those Who Need It Most</h2>
						<p>Dr. Taylor Stuteville is a licensed clinical psychologist and the founder of Slate Psychology, LLC, based in Overland Park, Kansas. She earned her Doctor of Psychology (PsyD) from Kansas City University of Medicine and Biosciences, where her doctoral research focused on the effects of diaphragmatic breathing interventions on shooting accuracy within law enforcement populations.</p>

						<p>Prior to her doctoral work, Dr. Stuteville earned her Bachelor of Arts in Psychology from the University of Kansas. Her early career included serving as a Youth Specialist at Elizabeth Layton Center, where she provided therapeutic support to adolescents and children, building a strong foundation in working with diverse populations across the lifespan.</p>

						<h3>Specialized Focus on First Responders</h3>
						<p>Dr. Stuteville has developed a deep expertise in working with emergency responders, including law enforcement officers, firefighters, EMTs, and dispatchers. She understands the unique psychological demands placed on those who serve their communities in high-stakes environments and provides a therapeutic space that is both confidential and free of judgment.</p>

						<p>Her research with the Kansas City Regional Police Academy demonstrated the measurable benefits of integrating breathing techniques into high-pressure performance situations, reflecting her commitment to practical, evidence-based strategies that her clients can apply both on and off duty.</p>

						<h3>Clinical Approach</h3>
						<p>Dr. Stuteville believes in helping individuals discover their full potential by focusing on strategies to improve everyday life. Her practice is grounded in evidence-based therapeutic approaches, and she works with both children and adults presenting with a wide range of concerns, including:</p>
						<ul class="approach-list">
							<li>Post-traumatic stress and occupational trauma</li>
							<li>Anxiety and depression</li>
							<li>Chronic pain management</li>
							<li>Stress and burnout</li>
							<li>Grief and loss</li>
							<li>Life transitions and adjustment</li>
							<li>Performance optimization under pressure</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>Practice &amp; Affiliations</h3>
						<p>In addition to her private practice through Slate Psychology, LLC, Dr. Stuteville is affiliated with Enso Therapy Group in the Kansas City area. She maintains offices in Overland Park, KS, conveniently located to serve the greater Kansas City metropolitan community.</p>

						<div class="bio-cta">
							<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
							<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/taylor-stuteville-2a7720126/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">View LinkedIn Profile</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.page-hero {
		background: var(--slate-900);
		color: var(--white);
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}
	.page-hero .section-label {
		color: var(--teal-400);
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.page-hero h1 {
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.page-hero-desc {
		color: var(--slate-400);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.bio-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}
	.bio-photo {
		position: sticky;
		top: 8rem;
	}
	.bio-photo-placeholder {
		background: var(--slate-100);
		border-radius: 16px;
		aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: var(--slate-400);
		gap: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.credentials-card {
		background: var(--bg-secondary);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}
	.credentials-card h4 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
	}
	.credentials-card ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.credentials-card li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}
	.credentials-card li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}
	.credentials-card strong {
		color: var(--text-primary);
	}

	.bio-content h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.bio-content h3 {
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.375rem;
	}
	.bio-content p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
	.approach-list {
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}
	.approach-list li {
		padding: 0.25rem 0;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
	.bio-cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.bio-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.bio-photo {
			position: static;
		}
		.bio-photo-placeholder {
			max-height: 300px;
		}
	}
</style>
